{
  "text": "In the first 30-min of the lower panel in Figure described by [CITATION_1] and by Leblanc and Rubio [ 19821 and called 'I n-events\" by Carr et al. (1983) . These bands may actually be a train of unresolved s-bursts, but since that identification cannot be made unambiguously with the Voyager data, we have not included such events in our s-burst data set.",
